text: Yasinta Aurellia (Hanacaraka: ꦪꦱꦶꦤ꧀ꦠꦄꦲꦸꦫꦺꦭ꧀ꦭꦶꦪ; born October 2, 2003) is an Indonesian beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Puteri Indonesia Lingkungan 2023. She represented Indonesia at the Miss Supranational 2023 pageant in Malopolska, Poland and finished in the top 24. == References == Category:Living people Category:Indonesian actors Category:Modeling (profession) Category:2003 births
title: Yasinta Aurellia
